                        </svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <p class="mt-8 text-base text-gray-400 md:mt-0 md:order-1">
                    &copy; <span id="year"></span> Shhhhhkeys. All rights reserved.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>

